Usage: run ev3_test_server.exe [optional port] (as admin - or it will be unable to bind itself to port)
Where 1234 is number of port. Server will automatically bind to localhost
(which in nancy means 0.0.0.0 - so all ip addresses).

(Under Linux / Mac OS X run using mono: mono ev3_test_server.exe [optional port])
Mono version 3.x required.

In this version graphic overview of projected robot movement is added.